    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m finally parting with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this beauty is practically flawless\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, you won\u2019t find a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere. It\u2019s been garage-kept and loved, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will appreciate it just as much as I have. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
