    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double VANOS system. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. Mechanical integrity is paramount; the VANOS unit has been professionally overhauled with upgraded seals, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to exceed factory structural specifications. The chassis remains rigid, showing no signs of fatigue or oxidation. Finished in Carbon Black Metallic over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the interior exhibits zero bolster wear and retains its factory matte finish. Documentation includes a comprehensive service history confirming preventative rod bearing replacement. This is a turn-key, investment-grade specimen for the discerning purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "One owner. Garage kept. Original paint. No accidents. Interior flawless. Mechanically perfect. Full service records included.",
      "price": 48500.0,
