    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a pristine, investment-grade example that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster, completely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections; the body panels are laser-straight with perfect factory gaps. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new, featuring supple leather upholstery with no bolster wear and a dashboard that has never been exposed to harsh UV rays. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the seat heaters, functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, backed by a complete service dossier and a spotless undercarriage that has never seen inclement weather. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to acquire a showroom-quality vehicle that has been maintained with an uncompromising attention to detail.",
      "price": 44900.0,
