      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present this meticulously preserved vehicle, currently offered in showroom condition. This unit has been maintained to the most exacting standards, exhibiting no discernible wear or compromise to its aesthetic and mechanical integrity. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a history of superior stewardship. This is an exceptional opportunity for the discerning buyer seeking a vehicle that remains indistinguishable from its original factory state. Professional inspections are welcomed and encouraged.",
