    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot. I've babied it since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and it\u2019s never missed a service. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the showroom price tag, you\u2019ve found it! It's super clean and ready for its next adventure. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
